PERIMETER&nbsp;SCAN&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></td>
<td align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="white"><font color="black" 
face="Arial,Sans-serif" size="2"><a href="#perim0">Firefox is becoming a more important target</a></font></td></tr>

<tr><td align="right" valign="top" bgcolor="white" width="1%" nowrap>
<font face="Arial,Sans-serif" size="2">&nbsp;</font></td>
<td align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="white"><font color="black" 
face="Arial,Sans-serif" size="2"><a href="#perim1">A bug fix for Firefox 2.0.0.4</a></font></td></tr>

